# paraisoDark Theme Demo
Output examples/svgs/themes/paraisoDark.svg

Set Theme paraisoDark
Set Template macos
Set Title "paraisoDark"
Set FontSize 14

Type "echo 'Welcome to the paraisoDark theme!'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "echo 'This is how your terminal looks.'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s
